item.title: AI Engineer Roadmap
item.description: Modified: August 02 2024 A resource by Code Basics We’ll see how this works. Starting in June of 2024, I plan to get myself prepared for a new career after another year of teaching. Pretty much; I want to find a job ideally that starts in the late summer of next year. Week 0 is stupid lol. Week 1 and 2 (6/2 - 6/17) I have a masters degree in this subject.
